        <section data-theme="light" class="faq">
          <div class="padding-global">
            <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-lg w-container">
              <div class="hflex-between-top is-faq">
                <div class="faq_left">
                  <div class="section-subtitle">
                    <div class="section-subtitle-dot"></div>
                    <div class="text-weight--medium text-style-uppercase">FAQs</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="spacer-24px"></div>
                  <h2>To clear out your questions</h2>
                  <div class="spacer-80px"></div>
                  <div class="hflex-left-center is-faq">
                    <div class="heading-style-h5 text-weight--medium">Still have questions?</div>
                    <div class="button-main-wrap">
                      <div class="button-click-area">
                        <a internal-link="var(--background--light)" target="" href="/../contact" class="button-link w-inline-block"><span class="button-text">Send us a message</span></a><button type="button" class="button-main">
                          <div class="button-text">Button Text</div>
                        </button>
                      </div>
                      <div aria-hidden="true" class="primary-button">
                        <div class="button-main-text">Send us a message</div>
                        <div class="button-main-text is-animation">1-minute form</div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="spacer-24px"></div>
                  <p>Response should be expected in 2 - 3 working days</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq_right">
                  <div class="faq_item">
                    <div class="spacer-24px"></div>
                    <div class="faq_item_question">
                      <h3 class="heading-style-h5 text-weight--medium">What kind of graphic design services do you offer?</h3>
                      <div class="faq_item_icon">
                        <div class="faq_item_icon_line1">
                          <div></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_item_icon_line2">
                          <div></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq_item_answer">
                      <div class="spacer-24px"></div>
                      <p>We handle a wide range of digital design needs: logos, brand kits, social media graphics, pitch decks, event materials, and more. If it needs to look amazing and match your brand&#x27;s personality, we’ve got you covered.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="spacer-24px"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="faq_item">
                    <div class="spacer-24px"></div>
                    <div class="faq_item_question">
                      <h3 class="heading-style-h5 text-weight--medium">I’m not sure what I need. Can you help?</h3>
                      <div class="faq_item_icon">
                        <div class="faq_item_icon_line1">
                          <div></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_item_icon_line2">
                          <div></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq_item_answer">
                      <div class="spacer-24px"></div>
                      <p>Absolutely! Many clients come to us with a fuzzy vision, that’s totally okay. We’ll help clarify your goals, explore creative directions, and recommend the best design assets to move your brand forward. Exactly as what we aim for to be your design partner.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="spacer-24px"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="faq_item">
                    <div class="spacer-24px"></div>
                    <div class="faq_item_question">
                      <h3 class="heading-style-h5 text-weight--medium">How long does it take to complete a design project?</h3>
                      <div class="faq_item_icon">
                        <div class="faq_item_icon_line1">
                          <div></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_item_icon_line2">
                          <div></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq_item_answer">
                      <div class="spacer-24px"></div>
                      <p>It really depends on what you need! A logo? 1 week. A full brand identity? Usually 2 weeks. Social media graphics? Often just a few days. Once we know your scope and timeline, we’ll give you a clear schedule.<br><br>And if you need to have a streamlined, continuous source of graphic designs, check out our Subscription model. A 1 price for all your design needs solution.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="spacer-24px"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="faq_item">
                    <div class="spacer-24px"></div>
                    <div class="faq_item_question">
                      <h3 class="heading-style-h5 text-weight--medium">Can you work with my existing brand?</h3>
                      <div class="faq_item_icon">
                        <div class="faq_item_icon_line1">
                          <div></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_item_icon_line2">
                          <div></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq_item_answer">
                      <div class="spacer-24px"></div>
                      <p>Of course! Whether you’ve got a full brand guide or just a logo on a napkin, we can adapt and design assets that align with your existing look and feel. Or, if you’re ready for a refresh, we’re happy to elevate your visual identity for a new journey ahead.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="spacer-24px"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="faq_item">
                    <div class="spacer-24px"></div>
                    <div class="faq_item_question">
                      <h3 class="heading-style-h5 text-weight--medium">How many revisions are included?</h3>
                      <div class="faq_item_icon">
                        <div class="faq_item_icon_line1">
                          <div></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_item_icon_line2">
                          <div></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq_item_answer">
                      <div class="spacer-24px"></div>
                      <p>We include up to two rounds of revisions in every project to make sure the design feels just right. Need more tweaks? No problem, we’ll always discuss extra revisions upfront so there are zero surprises.<br><br>Better yet, you can choose our subscription model to eleminate the revision hassle. Unlimited revision until you are completely happy with the design.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="spacer-24px"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="faq_item">
                    <div class="spacer-24px"></div>
                    <div class="faq_item_question">
                      <h3 class="heading-style-h5 text-weight--medium">What tools do you use?</h3>
                      <div class="faq_item_icon">
                        <div class="faq_item_icon_line1">
                          <div></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_item_icon_line2">
                          <div></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq_item_answer">
                      <div class="spacer-24px"></div>
                      <p>Our toolkit includes Figma and Affinity for most of our works. We do not use Adobe as we believe tools for design should be more transparent and less predatory.<br><br>We also utilize AI tools like MidJourney and ChatGPT for visual exploration and quick iteration.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="spacer-24px"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="faq_item">
                    <div class="spacer-24px"></div>
                    <div class="faq_item_question">
                      <h3 class="heading-style-h5 text-weight--medium">Will I have input during the design process?</h3>
                      <div class="faq_item_icon">
                        <div class="faq_item_icon_line1">
                          <div></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_item_icon_line2">
                          <div></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq_item_answer">
                      <div class="spacer-24px"></div>
                      <p>Of course! It&#x27;s your branding not ours!<br><br>At the end of the day, we understand that you are the biggest audience of your own branding, and it has to make you happy about it.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="spacer-24px"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="faq_item">
                    <div class="spacer-24px"></div>
                    <div class="faq_item_question">
                      <h3 class="heading-style-h5 text-weight--medium">How does design subscription work?</h3>
                      <div class="faq_item_icon">
                        <div class="faq_item_icon_line1">
                          <div></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_item_icon_line2">
                          <div></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq_item_answer">
                      <div class="spacer-24px"></div>
                      <p>Subscription is the type of payment that instead of paying for the whole service, you pay for the service in smaller parts.<br><br>For design, when you subscribe to a design service. You can add as many task as you want, revise as many time as it’s needed until it’s perfectly match your needs. This provide a flexibility that traditional fixed rate could not. As you can cancel the service anytime, no contract, no restriction.<br><br>Let’s say your startup is planning to cut on the design budget to funnel more into development, you can cancel the subscription with us and therefore, continue your business plan with no problem. Compared to traditional fixed rate, you will have to wait for the contract to expire which might hurt your business more. Especially for small to medium businesses and startups, where being flexible and the ability to change and adapt is seriously important.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="spacer-24px"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        
